WSL ------------- Windows Subsystem for Linux   

================

permissions -------------- file permissions
group ------------------- group
owner ------------------- owner
user -------------------- user
group owner ------------- group owner
world ------------------- world
everyone --------------- everyone
root -------------------- root
sudo -------------------- sudo
su ---------------------- su
sudo su ----------------- sudo su
sudo su root ------------ sudo su root  


windows ------- win
linux --------- linux----ubuntu/centos/redhat/suse/debian/arch
mac ----------- mac

